
### 1. GET All Products with Supplier and Category (deep expand)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$expand=supplier,category
Content-Type: application/json


### 2. GET Product Catalog View (flat view with stock status)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/report/ProductCatalog?$orderby=price desc
Content-Type: application/json


### 3. GET Low Stock Alerts (calculated view)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/report/LowStockAlert
Content-Type: application/json


### 4. GET Order Report with filter by status
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/report/OrderReport?$filter=status eq 'Completed'&$orderby=totalAmount desc
Content-Type: application/json


### 5. GET Sales Orders with full expand (customer + items + items/product)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/SalesOrders?$expand=customer,items($expand=product)
Content-Type: application/json


### 6. GET Products filtered by price range and ordered by rating
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=price ge 10000 and price le 80000&$orderby=rating desc&$select=name,price,stock,rating
Content-Type: application/json


### 7. GET Customers with creditLimit above threshold
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Customers?$filter=creditLimit ge 500000&$orderby=name asc
Content-Type: application/json


### 8. GET Suppliers filtered by country
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Suppliers?$filter=country_code eq 'IN'&$select=name,contact,email,city
Content-Type: application/json


### 9. GET Sales Orders filtered by date range with expand
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/SalesOrders?$filter=orderDate ge 2024-03-01 and orderDate le 2024-03-10&$expand=customer,items($expand=product)&$orderby=orderDate asc
Content-Type: application/json


### 10. GET Categories with self-referencing parentCategory expand
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Categories?$expand=parentCategory&$orderby=name asc
Content-Type: application/json


### 11. GET Products with LOW STOCK status from ProductCatalog
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/report/ProductCatalog?$filter=stockStatus eq 'LOW STOCK'&$expand=supplier,category
Content-Type: application/json


### 12. POST Deep Insert - New Sales Order with Items
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/SalesOrders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderNumber": "ORD-2024-0005",
  "customer_ID": "C002",
  "orderDate": "2024-04-01",
  "netAmount": 84998.00,
  "taxAmount": 15299.64,
  "grossAmount": 100297.64,
  "currency_code": "INR",
  "status": "New",
  "items": [
    {
      "product_ID": "P001",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 75999.00,
      "netAmount": 75999.00
    },
    {
      "product_ID": "P005",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 8999.00,
      "netAmount": 8999.00
    }
  ]
}